OL,3,CCouncil leader calls for referendum on
OL,4,CMayoral election proposals
OL,6,FThe leader of Lancashire County
OL,7,FCouncil says the public should have
OL,8,Ftheir say on proposals to introduce an
OL,9,Felected Mayor to the region.
OL,11,FStephen Atkinson has asked the
OL,12,FGovernment to permit a "legally
OL,13,Fbinding" public vote on the issue, as
OL,14,Fwell as plans to dissolve 12 district
OL,15,Fauthorities.
OL,17,FOn Thursday 19 June, the Reform UK
OL,18,Fpolitician will meet with Local
OL,19,FGovernment Minister Jim McMahon to
OL,20,Fdiscuss the request, which he has
OL,21,Falready submitted via a letter.
