OL,6,FCounty Cllr Atkinson told a meeting of
OL,7,FLancashire's Combined County Authority
OL,8,F(CCA) that the position "should become
OL,9,Fclear" after the talks.
OL,11,FHe said Reform's "ideal" outcome was
OL,12,Ffor there to be a referendum as the
OL,13,Fpreferred mechanism by which to
OL,14,Fundertake "a wide consultation".
OL,16,FThe devolution deal was signed last
OL,17,Fyear by the leaders of Lancashire
OL,18,FCounty Council and Blackpool and
OL,19,FBlackburn with Darwen councils.
