OL,6,FWhile the trio all concurred that the
OL,7,Fagreement was just the start of a
OL,8,Fdevolution journey, County Cllr
OL,9,FWilliamson never declared one way or
OL,10,Fthe other over whether her then Tory-
OL,11,Fled authority would ultimately accept
OL,12,Fa mayor ` noting simply that there was
OL,13,Fno consensus between all 15 leaders on
OL,14,Fthe issue.
OL,16,FMr McMahon had previously asked
OL,17,FLancashire local authorities to set
OL,18,Fout a shared vision for the county
OL,19,Fafter the councils they control are
OL,20,Fabolished, but so far no consensus has
OL,21,Fbeen reached.
